Comment: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.74,title,*screen,0413,0133,0050,,     [ Cue ]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:55.35,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, are you all here, you boneheads?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:57.83,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,As I'm gonna be a director an all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:01.87,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,I want a rating of \nover 20% so work your...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.36,0:02:04.29,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,asses off...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:15.80,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Geeze, we are starting the show in half an hour, why isn't anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:20.15,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we got our notices \n2 hours before the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:25.28,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,It's unbelievable that they all are so unmotivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.37,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ume-san! It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:36.35,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,You're assigned here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.30,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we the lucky ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:47.61,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,I was reassigned to this crappy show after directing a high-rated show which I worked on for the last 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:49.59,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:50.88,*Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:57.43,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Izumi-chan! You were put here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.31,*Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,They ordered me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.22,*Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,These are the CDs we're airing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:04.64,*Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote the name of the songs and the timings on the cue sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:13.91,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,What an unmotivated girl. She didn't even apologize for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:17.01,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't complain because she's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.94,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do with this\n unfocused rage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:21.26,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.63,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to turn my anger towards you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:27.35,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:29.56,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:33.59,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Densuke, aren't you suppose to say\n "I'm sorry for being late"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:38.24,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,You've made a quite an entrance\n for a clumsy Assistant Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:40.59,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm.. sorry for being late
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:44.83,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna know the kind of \nperson I hate the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:47.21,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,The person who's late for a work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.27,0:03:48.07,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:51.00,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,The person who is \nhandsome but useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.27,*Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than being ugly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.79,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,...wish I didn't hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.85,*Default,Densuke,0188,0177,0147,,{\c&HFFFF00&}Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:04:01.27,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Quit complaining! \nYou're just an A.D.!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.37,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF00&}This is just plain rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:04.64,*Default,Mattsuan,0056,0050,0035,,I can see how unmotivated you all are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:08.37,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,You can complain when you've \nbecome a real director!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:13.30,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Morning! Whoa, Mattsuan's director?\n Guess this show is going to be a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:16.91,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Densuke, you're being picked on \nas usual. Looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:21.12,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Ume-san is the mixer?\n Being reticence makes you look sharp.\n Come on, make some noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:25.53,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, nice sound effect! \nWith my script, Ume-san's sound effect, and Mattsuan being a director,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:29.77,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,we will win this year's Pulitzer award which has got nothing to do with it though. \nThis is so exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.49,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-chan, wanna go out for a\n drink after the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:33.18,*Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:34.96,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Ume-san~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:38.32,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Nice timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:41.05,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suga! Is the script done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:45.56,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. Who do you think I am? \nI am Suga-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:50.90,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}the legendary scenario writer \nwho had success in the "Live to the World! From Across the Antarctic" .
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.73,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\c&HFFFF00&}That's the program you\n worked on 10 years ago....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:56.21,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Just take a look at this. It's the revival of a legend. It's shining brightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:05:00.34,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,"Jump Out, MAICO!!"?\n Who the hell is MAICO?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:03.38,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please. She's the DJ of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:07.55,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,And I did it without even \nmeeting the DJ, It's brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:10.03,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Did we have any \nannouncer named MAICO?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:14.34,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,I know her! I think the name of the lady from the cigarette store across  from my apartment is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:19.75,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,"Good evening, everybody. My name is MAICO, the DJ of this show."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:24.19,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm an android working for the Nihon Broadcasting Corporation."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:27.16,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,"Two thumbs up for an android. An android is the greatest. An android, \ngotta catch' em all."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:30.09,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is THIS!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:36.81,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't it cool? A show that's run by an android. The first revolutionary show in the radio world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:39.12,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,This is where the legend begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:42.81,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Who came up with \nthis crappy idea? Who!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:46.49,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Of course Masuda Masu,\n the chief director.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.80,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,She's also legendary, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.39,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,What's so legendary about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:58.90,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,For the last 15 years, I've been solving thousands of people's problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:04.87,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's the company's orders, I can't make a fake show for all the listeners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.45,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer raising tomatoes back at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:14.62,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,This fraud is inexcusable. How can they come up with such a radio talk show!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:21.00,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,Think I would come up\n with a nonsense project!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:25.68,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,This is the project Nihon Broadcasting Corporation is giving everything they've got
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.99,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,to survive through the low-rated radio world of the 21st century.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:34.40,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,That's this show using an android as DJ, "Jump out, MAICO! 2010".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:54.53,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,This android will decide the future of Nihon Broadcasting Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:07:00.77,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,And you guys are the best of the best to make the show succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.84,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,A capable director who ran the life consultation show for 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:07.39,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,The reticent mixer with \nmany different techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.59,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,The scenario writer with\n many great ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:16.97,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,The specialist in song and sound selection. The useless assistant director "AD". And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:23.07,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you saying anything about me, Masuda Masu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:27.90,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,Please say I'm the program coordinator who pushes the show with revolutionary idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.10,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:29.96,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,God, no....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:33.86,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, so you're saying that \na robot is in this box?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:40.31,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a robot. It's fully automated intelligent android. The name is MAICO.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.57,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,This is an android...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:07.67,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,She's cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.29,*Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you got a crush on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:17.15,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,MAICO, you're awesome!\n She looks so real! This is great! \nHow does she look underneath?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.80,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,Ya wanna look?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:22.39,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,It's like looking at the \ndoll from a low angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:23.87,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're saying man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:25.84,*Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Men, what a foolish existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:30.39,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,The secret of MAICO will be revealed. It must be brightly shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.18,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.14,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF00&}Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:33.32,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HC080FF&}Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.52,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,S..she's not complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:46.03,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have enough time to finish her up. The bottom half will be completed in 2 weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:49.76,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,We only have 10 minutes \ntill the air time. Get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:55.24,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey! Are you saying that we must air the show with this freak!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:56.93,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you picking on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.17,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.20,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,And Densuke, you are fired as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:02.27,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:06.27,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait Matsu-san, if we don't start the show, I'm gonna be the one in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:08.44,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Just write up your resignation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.85,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.06,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,You are so easy to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:16.88,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,Even though MAICO is not complete, \nwe can still activate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:21.12,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think this is the part to show the ability of a capable director?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.33,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Densuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:23.84,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:24.95,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,That robot broad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.15,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,She's an android.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:30.05,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,She's nothing but a robot broad to me! So just activate that robot broad Densuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:30.83,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:34.29,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think you are an assistant director? We don't have enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:35.29,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.15,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,We have less than 5 \nminutes left! Move your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:39.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:44.08,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start the show \nwith S-2 as usual. And....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.77,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry up for my sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:50.28,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,First turn the main switch on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:57.35,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why isn't she moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:10:01.79,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,She won't move unless you install the OS! Don't you know that, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:06.21,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,These 50 CDs are the OS application discs! Hurry, up the show's gonna start!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:09.00,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:13.72,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying it's my fault? You, an ordinary AD, are blaming me, the program coordinator?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.58,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Move your ass, Densuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.92,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,We only have 3 minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:18.92,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,But still....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:23.40,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,Use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.75,*Default,*screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKidprint\fs32\c&HFFFFFF&}MAICO Activation Disc                                                 for Word Processor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:29.33,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,It says "for Word processor"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.47,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,What time do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.33,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Densuke, is that robot broad active?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.43,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:45.57,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it isn't good enough! Don't tell me she can't read the scripts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:52.29,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's looking good. It seems that she recognizes optically with CCD cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:59.66,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a data modem, exciting talk system, emergency shutdown system, and an emotional response control system.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:03.28,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your techno-babble. Densuke,\n place her in the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:05.49,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,How am I..?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:09.76,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Use your brain! Just carry \nher in or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.45,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,She's..heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.80,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Having trouble, Densuke-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.83,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Can't..you help...me....?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:20.93,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,MAICO is in the studio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.34,*Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,10 seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:26.31,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,No rehearsal but, we have no \nchoice! You got that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:27.75,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,She's ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:28.92,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,Ume-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:31.96,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.65,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:47.99,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:59.50,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,E...English...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:00.95,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,She's not fluent at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:05.05,*Default,Mattsuan,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't trust a machine\n with more than four frick'in buttons!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.87,*Default,Suga,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, MAICO. You're doing \nfine, you're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:11.29,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,The show... the show is ruined...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:16.70,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,It must be from the show's sponsor.\n Please answer the phone, \nMasuda Masu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:17.49,*Default,Masuda,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.70,*Default,Kattsuchin,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.42,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,She's...heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:28.69,*Default,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this show is \ngoing to work out...
